extends layout.pug

block content

  article.portfolio-intro

    h1 Let's make the web great together!

    p This portfolio highlights some of my skills as a developer.

  article.portfolio-project-thumbs
    .projects-box.box.grid

    each project in projects 

      a(href=`/projects/${project.id}`)
        h2= project.Random_Quote_Generator
        img(src=`${project.image_url}` width='320' height='240')

      .cell
        a(href='#')
          img.thumbnail(src='https://placehold.it/550x550' alt='')
          h5 My Site

